Priority: Normal
Severity: Minor
Reproducibility: Always
Platform: LG-X145
OS: Android
OS Version: 4.4.2

Summary: The search field is located in the top right side of the screen in the currency list

Description: The search field is located in the top right side of the screen in the currency list after clicking
on the currency selecting menu

Steps To Reproduce:

1. Open the "Convert Currency" application
2. Click on the selecting currency menu
3. Pay attention to the search field location

Actual result: The search field is located in the top right side of the screen in the currency list after clicking
on the currency selecting menu

Expected result: The search field is located in the top middle of the screen in the currency list after clicking
on the currency selecting menu

